{"tid":2422704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"可愛甜心鄭家純榮登三甲！白滑傲人上圍羡煞旁人！","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T13:07:32.000Z","uid":171094,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0192b187a19d934d0ce2954068d103626fd15a","tid":2422704,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYqVd3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYqVd3e.jpg&h=f8944b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcNkp9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcNkp9U.jpg&h=d001686f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYvRwN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYvRwN5.jpg&h=bbd59ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n福布斯公布最新香港富豪榜，長和創辦人李嘉誠以354億美元財富，再度成為香港首富，整體財富增長20%，受惠於其持股的Zoom帶來的增長，抵銷長實集團股價下挫27%的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">三甲亦包括恒地創辦人李兆基及新世界主席鄭家純，兩者分別以305億美元和221億美元，排行第2及第3。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於手機玻璃製造商伯恩光學的楊建文和林惠英，以186億美元排名第4，智能電話屏幕玻璃需求增長，帶動其財富增長逾1倍。<br />\n<br />\n其餘排名首10位的本港富豪，包括銀河娛樂主席呂志和、李錦記主席李文達、九倉大股東吳光正、華人置業創辦人劉鑾雄、新地鄺肖卿，以及阿里巴巴副主席蔡崇信。<br />\n<br />\n福布斯指，雖然香港去年經濟收縮6.1%，但股市造好，帶動香港首50名富豪的財富，增長7.5%至3310億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577422-20210225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577422-20210225.htm&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=d9a0a1ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577422-20210225.htm&h=55a8ca6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577422-20210225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cb8bdde0c374ecb95a6628edec26abe1d9fe72","tid":2422704,"uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTim